QuestData.Title: Chicken Party!
QuestData.Description: I bet you not guess what happen again.$B$BNope, not Goregek or chickens.$B$BOkay, I lie. Goregek let chickens out again. Dumb Goregek and rumbly belly.$B$BLet me know if you need help from any of the hunters... they around here somewhere.
QuestData.LogDescription: Capture 12 Chicken Escapees for Elder Harkek at Frenzyheart Hill.
QuestData.CompletionText: Chickens not get far usually... if wasps not eat them, maybe we just let them stay on field next time.
QuestData.RewardText: You good at this.$b$bMaybe someday we just dump Goregek in river so you not have to do this no more.
